original_font_information.description: The Quitador Sans typeface family is the perfect complement to Arne Freytags Quitador Slab design. The design traits of non-connecting bowl strokes and square shoulders in his slab serif are also at home in Quitador Sans. These distinctive features separate the design from many other sans serifs at large sizes. While at small sizes, they almost disappear leaving an inviting design suitable for a variety of interactive and print textual content.
